# What is Language AI?

Language AI is a branch of Artificial Intelligence that enables computers to understand, process, and generate human language.
It uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Large Language Models (LLMs) to interact with users.
Language AI can answer questions, translate languages, summarize text, and generate content.
It learns from large amounts of text data to understand context and meaning.
Examples include ChatGPT, Gemini, and Claude.
Language AI is widely used in chatbots, virtual assistants, and content generation.



